summary: This Small mods adds a new armour and some new weapons the armour is invincible and the weapons are legendary. You can find the weapons and armour at the Camo Camp marked on your map just west of Whiterun, this is my second mod so I hope you guys like it, I\'d like it if you could send me some names for an arena (rude or not) thanks!
